snippet.title: High Times - Teaser Trailer (VO Main Cast)
snippet.description:
Manage your own donut café in High Times, and help customers escape from their problems by serving special donuts that affect their emotions. Sometimes they don't know what they want, so listen to their stories, offer them advice in the form of donuts, and mend broken relationships.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2251220/
Support us on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/yangyangmobile/high-times

Voice Cast (main exes):
*Nola Klop as MJ
*LilyPichu as Lucy
*Johnny Yong Bosch as Harry
*Ciaran Strange as Emmette
*Aife as Stacy
